            {"q": "Which of the following is a biome? I. Aquatic habitat II. Swamps III. Savannah IV. Mangrove forest", "opts": ["I and II", "III only", "III and IV", "All of the above"], "ans": 2, "exp": "Biomes are large-scale ecosystems. Savannah (grassland biome) and Mangrove forest are recognized biomes."},
            {"q": "In bacteria, conjugation involves: I. Transfer of plasmid DNA II. Sexual reproduction III. F+ to F- bacteria IV. No genetic recombination", "opts": ["I and III", "II only", "I and IV", "All of the above"], "ans": 0, "exp": "Bacterial conjugation involves transfer of plasmid DNA (I) from F+ (donor) to F- (recipient) bacteria (III). It is NOT true sexual reproduction."},
