            {"q": "Which process describes liquid turning into gas at any temperature?", "opts": ["Boiling", "Evaporation", "Condensation", "Sublimation"], "ans": 1, "exp": "Evaporation occurs at any temperature at the surface of a liquid. Boiling occurs throughout the liquid at a specific temperature."},
