            {"q": "A rainbow viewed through a blue sheet of glass appears:", "opts": ["White", "Yellow", "Blue", "Black"], "ans": 2, "exp": "A blue filter only transmits blue light. When the rainbow (white light components) passes through a blue filter, only the blue component is transmitted."},
